"Applies to the kube API servers from this workspace's kubeconfigs (e.g. `kubectl delete` fails cleanly)." = "適用於此工作區 kubeconfig 中的 kube API 伺服器（例如 `kubectl delete` 會乾淨地失敗）。";
"All *.amazonaws.com APIs; classified by action name (Delete*/Terminate* = destructive, Get*/List*/Describe* = read)." = "所有 *.amazonaws.com API；依操作名稱分類（Delete*/Terminate* = 破壞性，Get*/List*/Describe* = 讀取）。";
