"socket.dev and OSV only fire on artifact downloads (.tgz, .whl, .crate, …) — not on plain metadata fetches. Packages cached in npm/pip's local store don't hit the network at all." = "socket.dev 與 OSV 僅在下載實際套件檔（.tgz、.whl、.crate 等）時觸發，純粹的中繼資料請求不會觸發。已在 npm/pip 本機快取中的套件根本不會走網路。";

