"“Log but continue” records detections to the Security Log window. “Ask me what to do” pauses the request and shows the flagged text. “Block” fails the request outright." = "「記錄但繼續」會將偵測記錄到安全紀錄視窗。「詢問我該怎麼做」會暫停請求並顯示被標記的文字。「封鎖」會直接讓請求失敗。";
